            <p>Convert the following complex numbers to the form <m>a + bi</m>.</p>
            <ol cols="2">
                <li><p><m>2 \cis(\pi / 6 )</m></p></li>
                <li><p><m>5 \cis(9\pi/4)</m></p></li>
